Bernstein, Respondent, v. Cohen, Appellant. (Common Pleas of New York City and County, General Term. January 6, 1890.) Appeal from third district court.

Argued before Bookstaver, P. J., and Bischoff, J.

Benno Loewy, for appellant. M. Altenmeyer, for respondent.

No opinion. Ordered that the judgment be affirmed, with costs.
